dc_description_s: This data represents DNR managed land parcels in Wisconsin in 2023. [This dataset contains DNR Managed Lands as parcels with local property name, and GIS and deed acreages. Parcels are symbolized as fee simple (DNR Owned), DNR easement on private land (open/restricted public access) and DNR lease on federal- and county-owned land. This dataset does not contain closed fee or easement. See metadata/data dictionary for interest (transaction type) classification. The parcels are digitized from deed legal description and based on the DNR Landnet System (Public Land Survey System), Wisconsin Transverse Mercator. This data is updated on a weekly basis. This layer represents the geometry of the real estate holdings of the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources and is not to be interpreted as representing legal property boundaries.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit:https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/wi-dnr::dnr-managed-land-parcels/about
